            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of <strong>carrot 'ribbons'</strong></p>\r\n<p>Slice the <strong>radishes</strong> as finely as you can into thin rounds&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve half of the <strong>honey</strong> in 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> in a large bowl</p>\r\n<p>Once dissolved, add the <strong>rice vinegar</strong>&nbsp;and a pinch of salt&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> and <strong>chopped radishes</strong> and set aside until serving &ndash; this is your <strong>pickled carrot &amp; radish</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>noodles</strong> to a pot, cover with <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook over a high heat for 8-9 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Drain the <strong>noodles</strong>&nbsp;and run under <strong>cold water</strong> until cooled</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1324.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;in half</p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>soy sauce</strong>&nbsp;and juice of the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in a small bowl &ndash; this is your<strong> chilli &amp; lime dressing&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
